author: wyattwolf
title: who doesn't want another Batmobile
review:
I do enjoy collecting these polybag batmobiles so soon as I saw this in my local supermarket I had to get it. Kinda reminds me of the Tumbler, looks like it can batter its way through barricades and walls with ease.

Nice little build and will look good next to all my other batmobiles :)
